lt":false,"gender":0,"id":5265137,"known_for_department":"Editing","name":"Nazgul Omurzhanova","original_name":"Nazgul Omurzhanova","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"68b6fc7a1993120f591f2dc1","department":"Editing","job":"Editor"}]}},"person_4315025_translations":{"at":1773319438095,"data":{"id":4315025,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yosra Rebai","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AE","iso_639_1":"ar","name":"العربية","english_name":"Arabic","data":{"biography":"","name":"Yosra Rebai","primary":true}}]}},"person_3790135_translations":{"at":1773384111868,"data":{"id":3790135,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Charles Montalembert","primary":true}}]}},"person_2111474_translations":{"at":1773470201337,"data":{"id":2111474,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Chen Haoyu","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"2014年1月参加在台湾中视举办的《华人星光大道3》并获得总冠军 ，同年12月参加中央电视台《中国正在听》并获得全国8强而出道。\n\n　　2015年，参演两岸合拍的微电影《湄洲之夏》饰演性格开朗的女主角程舒怡。4月，参与《左耳》舞台剧演出。同年5月参演《小时代》音乐剧，在剧中扮演善良温和的林萧。\n\n　　2016年7月，参演《回到明朝当王爷之杨凌传》饰演敢爱敢恨的唐一仙，这也是其首次挑战古装角色。同年11月，在古装传奇剧《如懿传》中饰演了气度冷傲却十分痴情的舒妃叶赫那拉·意欢。\n\n　　2017年4月，主演了励志校园网络剧《热血高校》，剧中饰演元气少女郁佳。\n\n　　2019年7月，参演的古代传奇剧《九州缥缈录》开播，饰演足智多谋的少女政治家小舟。2019年10月，参演了电影《小山河》，饰演回乡创业的女大学生青禾。\n\n　　2020年1月，参演了悬疑科幻网剧《失踪人口》，饰演被困于神秘河谷的幸存者之一李翘。2020年5月，参演的青春校园剧《我才不要和你做朋友呢》开播，剧中饰演了仗义坦率的李青桐。","name":"陈昊宇","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Trần Hạo Vũ sinh ngày 7 tháng 4 năm 1992 tại Phúc Châu, Phúc Kiến, là nữ ca sĩ, diễn viên người Trung Quốc. Năm 2018, cô thủ vai Lý Kiều trong \"Mất Tích\". Năm 2017, cô thủ vai Tiểu Châu trong \"Cửu Châu: Phiêu Miểu Lục\" và Uất Giai trong \"Trung Học Nhiệt Huyết\". Năm 2016, cô thủ vai Diệp Hách Na Lạp Ý Hoan trong \"Như Ý Truyện\".","name":"Trần Hạo Vũ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"陳昊宇","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"2014 年 1 月參加在台灣中視舉辦的《華人星光大道 3》並獲得總冠軍 ，同年 12 月參加中央電視台《中國正在聽》並獲得全國 8 強而出道。\n\n2015 年，參演兩岸合拍的微電影《湄洲之夏》飾演性格開朗的女主角程舒怡。4 月，參與《左耳》舞台劇演出。同年 5 月參演《小時代》音樂劇，在劇中扮演善良温和的林蕭。\n\n2016 年 7 月，參演《回到明朝當王爺之楊淩傳》飾演敢愛敢恨的唐一仙，這也是其首次挑戰古裝角色。同年 11 月，在古裝傳奇劇《如懿傳》中飾演了氣度冷傲卻十分痴情的舒妃葉赫那拉·意歡。\n\n2017 年 4 月，主演了勵志校園網絡劇《熱血高校》，劇中飾演元氣少女鬱佳。\n\n2019 年 7 月，參演的古代傳奇劇《九州縹緲錄》開播，飾演足智多謀的少女政治家小舟。2019 年 10 月，參演了電影《小山河》，飾演回鄉創業的女大學生青禾。\n\n2020 年 1 月，參演了懸疑科幻網劇《尋人啟弒》，飾演被困於神秘河谷的倖存者之一李翹。2020 年 5 月，參演的青春校園劇《我才不要和你做朋友呢》開播，劇中飾演了仗義坦率的李青桐。","name":"陳昊宇","primary":false}}]}},"person_126667_translations":{"at":1773470204281,"data":{"id":126667,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"John Hunter Bell (born 20 October 1997) is a Scottish actor. He has played Bain in two instalments of The Hobbit film series, \"Young Ian\" Murray in the Starz television series Outlander, Angus in Battleship, Helius in Wrath of the Titans and Toby Coleman in Tracy Beaker Returns.","name":"John Bell","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"John Bell (* 20. Oktober 1997 in Paisley, Schottland) ist ein schottischer Schauspieler.\n\nBell begann im Alter von sieben Jahren in Glasgow mit dem Theaterspielen. Nach einer kleinen Rolle als Creet 2007 in der Doctor-Who-Folge Utopia spielte er seine erste Kinorolle 2009 in dem Film A Shine of Rainbows. Nachdem John Bell in verschiedenen Fernsehfilmen und Serien mitspielte, übernahm er Rollen in den beiden 2012 erschienenen Filmen Zorn der Titanen und Battleship. Er besucht das Royal Conservatoire of Scotland. In Der Hobbit: Smaugs Einöde und Der Hobbit: Die Schlacht der Fünf Heere übernahm er die Rolle des Bain. 2016 wurde er für die Rolle des jungen Ian Murray in Outlander gecastet.\n\nQuelle: Wikipedia","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"约翰·贝尔","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"約翰·貝爾","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Джон Белл","primary":false}}]}}}}